original_title: PFL Regular Season 2022 - PFL 6: Harrison vs Young
overview: Week 6 of the regular season happens tonight (Jul 1) in Atlanta, GA and features a main event between two-time PFL women’s lightweight champion Kayla Harrison and women’s MMA pioneer Kaitlin Young, who is filling in for the injured Julia Budd. The co-main event pits former UFC welterweight title challenger and ex-Bellator champion Rory MacDonald against Sadibou Sy.
title: PFL Regular Season 2022 - PFL 6: Harrison vs Young
